channel.title: Endar Problems
channel.description:
Yesterday I downloaded the new Endar with the 7955 cache. I double click 'Endar V4 Main Setup' and I get a rather long error. Cant upload on image shack, it's hating me ATM and wont let me upload anything. The error goes along the lines of this.
[code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.UnsupportedClassVersionError: EGUI <Unsupported major.minor version 49.0[/code]
And some other Java related jargon which I don't understand. So if anyone could possibly help, it would be greatly appreciated.
